#Required Software
===================
1. Java 1.6 or higher (1.7 recommended)
2. Maven 2 or higher
3. Intellij Idea or Eclipse

#How to Build
===============
mvn clean install

#How to run
============
1. Open Project in Intellij idea or eclipse
2. Open /mail.properties file in resource folder.
3. Add your personal email to `mail.username` and email password to `mail.password`.
4. Add from email address to `mail.from.address` (Use your email address to test)
5. Add to email address to `mail.to.address` (Use your email address to test)
6. Open TestApp.java (This contains test class for sending mail) and run main method

#Technologies Used
==================
1. akka
2. javax mail api
